data.description: Welcome to 3553 Saint Joachim in Saint Ann! This cute bungalow style home is  perfect  for a 1st time home buyer or someone down sizing. The home has gleaming hardwood floors through out featuring 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, a large family room and a separate dining room. The walk up unfinished basement is clean as a whistle and ready for your finishing touches. Large fenced in backyard with a one car detached garage.
